{"tid":831453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國調查 男性一生性伴侶比女性多一倍","createTime":"2018-09-22T03:17:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T15:02:53.000Z","uid":122,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ade0e44f62a5a07e894be3f20ee8b8777afc77e3","tid":831453,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T03:17:00.000Z","msg":"人一生通常只可以有一個終生伴侶，但性伴侶呢？似乎係可以無限。根據英國格拉斯哥大學一項調查就指出，男人平均會比女人多一倍！<br />\n<br />\n調查訪問咗15,000位年齡介於16至74歲嘅男女，得出平均值，男人平均有過14位性伴，而女人只有7位。而且其中有機會男人係比數字上多，因為幾乎大部分男人都忘記咗自己有過幾多位性伴侶，相反女性就通常都清楚記得。其中最多性伴嘅男士，擁有過110位伴侶，至於女士最多則有50位，又係差唔多男多女一倍！"},{"pid":"c2c5b1151ac5013f772dacb33064e02eb5b43832","tid":831453,"uid":102609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T03:26:52.000Z","msg":"Thisav嘅性伴侶緊係唔記得<br />\n撳完X就搵下個啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8347fb5f4fba05861bf40d38ef18b8c3a1d98569","tid":831453,"uid":64770,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T03:31:35.000Z","msg":"痴線 真係咁多gay佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e05d1c47b9693c6e7dbdaa7afb159f739dd41516","tid":831453,"uid":53577,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T03:33:54.000Z","msg":"女人唔講出嚟啫"},{"pid":"3272027fd041687401604560506b1c55fb977b28","tid":831453,"uid":73613,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T03:36:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"013922a939440e5e3a356eb1b1a44bba9cdc2ff7","tid":831453,"uid":61271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T03:36:49.000Z","msg":"平均14個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f23ed75b472ab80bd54fd3acbf99b40caa78ae","tid":831453,"uid":153867,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T03:38:03.000Z","msg":"點樣多一倍 搞基？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b63b05cb42bad6